cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.GT, cs.CC 

This paper deals with the computational complexity of joint subcarrier and power allocation problems in multi-carrier NOMA systems, which are related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), game theory (cs.GT), and computer communication (cs.CC). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
